  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      507.56,
      538.58,
      578.69
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in Western, Central, Sabaragamuwa and North-central provinces and in Galle, Matara and Vavuniya districts after 1.00 p.m. Showers or thundershowers may occur at a few places in the other areas of the island during the evening or night.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      586.73,
      538.01,
      619.25
    ],
    "text": "Showers may occur in coastal areas of Western province and in the Puttalam and Jaffna districts in the morning.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      0.9599999785423279,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      622.79,
      538.14,
      660.07
    ],
    "text": "Misty conditions can be expected at some places in Central, Sabaragamuwa and Uva provinces and in Ampara and Polonnaruwa districts during the early hours of the morning.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      663.13,
      537.98,
      699.43
    ],
    "text": "The general public is kindly requested to take adequate precautions to minimize damages caused by temporary localized strong winds and lightning during thundershowers.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      4.079999923706055,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      702.49,
      538.14,
      777.94
    ],
    "text": "On the apparent northward relative motion of the sun, it is going to be directly over the latitudes of Sri Lanka during 05th to 15th of April in this year. The nearest areas of Sri Lanka over which the sun is overhead tomorrow (07th) are Dehiwala, Maharagama, Pannipitiya, Padukka, Eheliyagoda, Maskeliya, Siyambalanduwa and Pottuvil about 12:13 noon.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
